(42, 5, 11, 41, 10, 21, 21, NULL, 'Call to Follow Jesus', 'Both passages emphasize the call to forsake worldly possessions and follow Jesus. In Luke, the disciples leave everything to follow Him, while in Mark, Jesus instructs the man to sell all he has and follow Him.', 'theme', 0.32799999999999996, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
