(42, 5, 12, 19, 50, 15, 15, 'Lord, if thou wilt, thou canst make me clean', 'Healing and Deliverance Connection', 'This connection highlights the theme of seeking help in times of distress. The leper''s plea for cleansing in Luke parallels the call to God for deliverance in Psalms.', 'theme', 0.356, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
